snippet.title: Horribunnies: Ophéline Reveal Trailer 💉🐇
snippet.description:
We are introducing Ophéline!💉  She's the one in charge of the back room of the petshop!
She loves bunnies just as much as Pâquerette... in her own way. 💸
Let's say she knows how to make bunnies turn into Horribunnies.. 🐇
